---
title: Chorizo & Roast Veggie Israeli Couscous with Caramelised Onion & Lemon Yoghurt
description: With roasted cauliflower and kumara, this colourful pearl couscous toss is the perfect midweek pick-me-up! The addition of flaked almonds, smokey chorizo and caramelised onion makes for an easy yet impressive dish.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5ed8326827795208c7273895-74389989.jpg
